text: A lot of fun with a few twists and a warning: be careful what you wish for, you might just get it. Because of the horror coated with humour, Fantasy Island is now one of my favourites movies. We liked the contrast between dark and scary scenes with light and humorous scenes. We feel the plot and structure of the film suited the fantasy feel, thus leaving confusion, if any, to our own fantasy and imagination. I would definitely recommend others to watch Fantasy Island, no matter your personal style and preference.
